<h1 align="center">Motihari College Of Engineering, Motihari</h1>
<p>Motihari college of Engineering (MCE),Motihari is a government college,fully funded by the government of Bihar.<br>
And It's affiliated to Aryabhatta Knowledge of University ( AKU) Patna and approved by AICTE(New Delhi).<br>
And it's allies under top 10th possition on bihar engineering college Previously the institue was known as Indian College of Engineering and was established on 24 November 1980.<br>
